These are proprietary NVIDIA products that are widely used in the ML systems
community. The MLOSS paper and cover letter justify this dependency. The open
claim of this project is the SCN inference path and the full
train→eval→export→deploy cookbook — not a CUDA/TensorRT-free stack.

